data.description: Are you looking for that special Christmas gift for your significant other or for yourself? Look no further. This spacious 3 bedroom ranch home in Possum Woods has many updates including laminate flooring throughout, an updated full and half bath on the main level, updated kitchen with appliances are included, new roof in 2021, living room and bedrooms have new windows in 2021, some new plumbing in 2021, updated electric to 200 amp service in 2022. Full semi finished basement has family room with additional fireplace, possible 4th bedroom, a large workshop area with laundry and plenty of cabinets for tons of storage. Property includes 2 parcels. One parcel is .60 acres and a second parcel 3000600002410006 is .55. All is fenced in with mature trees! Large storage shed. Deck off of the kitchen. More updates include Lenox furnace and AC approx. 7 years old. Hot water tank 4 years old, water softener in 2020 and new well bladder in 2020. Taxes include extra parcel. Schedule your private showing today!
